section.section:
The statement shall provide:
The reason for the license surrender;
For each consumer for whom the licensee is providing debt management services, the following information:
The name of the consumer;
The total amount of funds held by the licensee for distribution to the consumer's creditors; and
The name of each creditor of the consumer that is receiving payments from the licensee for debts owed by the consumer to the creditor, and the outstanding balance owed to each creditor.
